::KitKat::

She turned and looked at Land Mine.  "You can't make a mistake on a 
hunt. You simply learn as you go. Come along and I'll show you. And 
as far as punishment.  You punish yourself harder than I would ever 
have punished you.  Don't worry about punishment.  Just being on thid 
planet with this war is punishment enough."

be
